Laundry Attendant / Laundry Services Specialist

Our Laundry Services Specialists are responsible for ensuring all linens, towels, and garments are cleaned, pressed, and delivered in a timely manner to maintain hotel standards of cleanliness.

Browse Job Board   Contact us

Duties & Responsibilities:

  • Operate washing, drying, and pressing machines for linens and guest laundry.
  • Fold and organize linens for distribution to guest rooms and public areas.
  • Maintain cleanliness and orderliness of the laundry area.
  • Track laundry inventory and report any shortages.
  • Handle guest laundry requests with attention to detail.

Desired Qualifications:

  • Experience working in laundry operations or a similar environment preferred.
  • Familiarity with laundry machines and detergents.
  • Strong organizational skills and attention to detail.
  • Ability to work efficiently under pressure.
  • Physical stamina and ability to lift heavy loads.
